greenmirror.client.modelinitializers

Class GroovyScriptModelInitializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • greenmirror.client.modelinitializers.GroovyScriptModelInitializer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ModelInitializer

    public class GroovyScriptModelInitializer
extends java.lang.Object
implements ModelInitializer
    The model initializer that initializes the model through a Groovy script.

    Note that nodes are layered on the visualizer in the order in which they are added.

    Author:
    Karim El Assal
